      "comment_id" : 58949276,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "The instructions for migrating to Fabric specify referencing the Crashlytics artifact directly, presuming you are using that Fabric &quot;kit&quot;: <a href=\"https://fabric.io/migrations/gradle\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">fabric.io/migrations/gradle</a>"
    }, {
      "owner" : {
        "account_id" : 122115,
        "reputation" : 5378,
        "user_id" : 315702,
        "user_type" : "registered",
        "accept_rate" : 88,
        "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/714b68c7bd219bd9d4b777ba6d9f401d?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
        "display_name" : "Mark McClelland",
